snippet.textDisplay:
For anyone wanting information on charities, DO NOT DONATE TO THE AUSTRALIAN RED CROSS OR ST VINCENT DE PAULS OR THE AUSTRALIAN SALVATION ARMY as they are WITHOLDING DONATIONS made to them and lining their own pockets with them.

DONATE DIRECTLY TO THE STATE FIRE BRIGADES LIKE CFS, RFS, CFA and TFS to name a few

Foodbank is a better alternative to donate to instead of the Red Cross

Wildlife conservation projects and hospitals like the ARC (animal rescue collective) WIRES, Wildlife Victoria, Port Macquarie Koala Hospital.

The information is out there to donate, just please make sure to do extensive research to know where your money is going. And please stop donating to the three grubby charities because they aren’t providing the relief you all would hope for and have been squirrelling away your money for their own private means, not for our country or our affected communities.

snippet.textDisplay:
Hey Jack?
Thank you so fucking much.
Most of our donations aren’t even getting to the fire affected areas, only a small part of it is. Our wildlife is suffering, wombats are making intricate burrows and leading other animals into them to save them. Our PM fucked off to Hawaii at the start and now he’s doing barely anything to help. Some parts of the country are covered in thick smoke, we can’t breath. It’s even wafting overseas.

But we haven’t lost our Aussie Spirit! You’re help means a lot to us so thank you 💚
